QuestData.Title: Not Here, Not Now
QuestData.Description: I will travel to your people to make arrangements soon.$B$BFor now, begone. Leave me in peace.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Lieutenant Willem at Southport.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent. We have more immediate concerns to deal with until he visits.$B$BHulda Shadowblade requires your immediate attention, $Gsir:maam;.
